# Instagram Reels — First 30 Days

One reel per day, ~30-second production each. Mix of pain-led, education, trust-building, and conversion.

---

## Pillar mix (per week)

- 3 Pain-led (the hook)
- 2 Education (the value)
- 1 Trust (the proof)
- 1 Conversion (the ask)

---

## Week 1 — Pain reels (build the audience)

